summary: AIM ImmunoTech Inc has agreed to renew the lease with 604 Associates LLC for another year, extending the lease term to April 30, 2027, with a monthly rent of $3,100 starting May 1, 2026. The letter, dated October 16, 2025, was addressed to Lawrence R. Antonucci and signed by Peter W. Rodino, III, COO & General Counsel of AIM ImmunoTech Inc.
